Below is the **complete system-level breakdown** of:

# 🔷 LOGIC 3 – Procurement Need Definition and Structuring

---

# 1️⃣ PURPOSE OF THIS LOGIC

This logic converts:

> “We need something”
> into
> A structured, standardized, auditable procurement request

It ensures:

* Clear specifications
* Comparable bids
* Fair evaluation
* Budget control
* Reduced ambiguity
* Legal defensibility

If this logic is weak → evaluation becomes subjective, disputes increase, and procurement fails.

---

