# 1️⃣4️⃣ SYSTEM CONTROLS FOR FAIRNESS

To prevent manipulation:

* Criteria locked after publish
* Version control of requirements
* Change log visibility
* Public clarification log
* Amendment window with extension logic

If requirements amended:

* Deadline automatically extended

---

# 1️⃣5️⃣ QUALITY CONTROL VALIDATIONS

System prevents:

❌ Vague specs
❌ Unmeasurable KPIs
❌ Hidden criteria
❌ Brand favoritism
❌ Undefined deliverables
❌ Undefined payment terms

Prompts user if:

* Criteria weights incomplete
* Missing scope details
* No acceptance criteria
* No dispute clause

